	name = "Nanotrasen Asset Retention"
	description = "This branch of Nanotrasen specialises in personal protection, as well as protection of the corporation's interests and assets. \
	The branch has taken to hiring skilled veterans from both private and public military services but have begun \
	instituting training programs to breed their own operatives for the future. \
	Infamous among NT personell for the roumored \"deathsquads\" that they operate inside NT."
